        <q>¿Cómo podrían usar los cuadrados que tiene cada uno de estos rectángulos para encontrar el área de cada rectángulo?</q>  (In C, I can just count the tiles. In B, I could finish tiling the rectangle and count the tiles. In D I would need to straighten out the tiles so they cover all of the rectangle. In A, I could count the blue tiles and double the number since in each row there are the same number of white tiles as there are blue tiles.
